{"id":1735059,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:13.513Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735059,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Baru Nak Untung","overview":"# Baru Nak Untung (New Luck)  The story follows young people today who take their future for granted and depend on their parents for daily needs. Atan, Mior and Leman Afro, who have been close friends since childhood, happily go through life doing activities together and are willing to accept each other's good and bad sides. Unfortunately, they are unsuccessful in their jobs. Atan and Afro only spend their time playing music without any direction. Likewise, Mior became a company manager but was fired. They become unemployed and rely on financial assistance from their respective families. This situation worries Pak Salim, Atan's father. He wants to see his son succeed like other people's children and get suitable employment. Considering their interest in music, Pak Salim suggests they become buskers or street singers. At least they can earn honest income and at the same time, if they are lucky, their talent can be noticed by individuals involved in the music field.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/no9xc7vJlC0aqn4s9bSkb8Ivfz2.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Baru Nak Untung","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1810110,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Anas Ridzuan","original_name":"Anas Ridzuan","popularity":0.3348,"profile_path":"/gxIyE9EwsBK2yWonXQCgUsOo5sL.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5eb052dec9e8f3c7c0c8cb","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1280845,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Arja Le